  <section id="research" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Research Areas</h2>
      <div class="grid cols-3">
        <div class="card"><div class="card-inner">
          <div class="tag blue">Noise & Acoustics</div>
          <h3>Prediction & Mitigation</h3>
          <p>Bridging aeroacoustic models and community metrics (SEL, DNL, EPNL). Tools include FAA AEDT, NASA AIRNOISEUAM, Helios, PSU‑WOPWOP, and custom pipelines.</p>
        </div></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-inner">
          <div class="tag green">Routing</div>
          <h3>Dynamic Airspace Allocation</h3>
          <p>Multi‑objective optimization of AAM corridors with constraints for safety, equity, and noise exposure. A* / K‑shortest path diversity and altitude layering.</p>
        </div></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-inner">
          <div class="tag red">DAA</div>
          <h3>Vision‑Based Detect & Avoid</h3>
          <p>Training YOLOv9/v11 on AVOIDDS for intruder aircraft detection; analysis with precision‑recall, IoU, and confidence distributions.</p>
        </div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

