    <div class="container">
      <h2>Projects</h2>
      <div class="grid cols-3">
        <div class="card"><div class="card-inner">
          <div class="tag purple">Optimization</div>
          <h3>Noise‑Optimized AAM Routing</h3>
          <p>Horizontal & vertical optimization to reduce exposure around receptors; evaluates SEL/DNL improvements and equity impacts.</p>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="#">Code / Paper</a>
        </div></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-inner">
          <div class="tag orange">Tooling</div>
          <h3>UAM Noise Tooling Benchmark</h3>
          <p>Comparative study of AEDT, AIRNOISEUAM, Helios, PSU‑WOPWOP, and others; taxonomy and use‑case guidance.</p>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="#">Repo</a>
        </div></div>
        <div class="card"><div class="card-inner">
          <div class="tag blue">Computer Vision</div>
          <h3>DAA with YOLOv9/YOLOv11</h3>
          <p>Training and evaluation on AVOIDDS: intruder aircraft detection, confusion analysis, and PR curves for publication.</p>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="#">Results</a>
        </div></div>
      </div>
